{"tid":2131061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新攬炒系列27: 本港第2季經濟初值按年收縮9%","createTime":"2020-07-29T14:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T02:02:50.000Z","uid":292292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d30e7509a786eaf59e2c937d34bbc36c5be102d5","tid":2131061,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540573-20200729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540573-20200729.htm&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=9026fd19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540573-20200729.htm&h=516f5684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540573-20200729.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府統計處的數據顯示，第2季本地生產總值預先估計按年實質下跌9%，差過市場預期，主要是內部及對外需求均持續疲弱，但跌幅較首季修定後的收縮9.1%略為收窄。<br />\n<br />\n至於經季節性調整而作相連季度比較的本地生產總值，第2季較第1季實質輕微下跌0.1%。<br />\n<br />\n上季私人消費開支按年實質下跌14.5%，跌幅較首季的10.6%加劇。政府消費開支繼首季上升8.8%後，上季按年實質上升9.6%。<br />\n<br />\n上季貨品出口總額按年跌2.1%，跌幅較首季的9.7%顯著收窄。上季貨品進口實質下跌6.8%，亦較首季跌幅11.1%為小。上季服務輸出按年下跌46.6%，跌幅較首季的37.4%擴大。上季服務輸入下跌43.5%，亦較首季跌24.5%為多。"},{"pid":"44e88a7a138126b47525b6717cfeb17bbdae9da9","tid":2131061,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"死藍絲"},{"pid":"ad547090a8892cd345bd3750e2f59ae571420232","tid":2131061,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"第三季仲大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b5f9fa6240605834a12b97ea94d45b083db730","tid":2131061,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:02:50.000Z","msg":"金融肺炎，勁過金融海嘯"}]}